{"tid":531772,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"新年前定新年後遞信","createTime":"2018-01-17T07:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T13:52:01.000Z","uid":9205,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"66f3f876b119055cdcf157767a2dc8d0e1238c95","tid":531772,"uid":9205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:36:46.000Z","msg":"我公司既傳統係臨到新年先出花紅<br />\n即係年29/年30先出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做左幾年覺得悶想轉換環境<br />\n但如果出完花紅個日即遞好似好串 唔知會唔會寫衰份reference letter<br />\n過左新年差唔到要初七 再捱多一個月<br />\n<br />\n因為我夜晚返夜校 份工又on shift 搞到有時要走堂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新年前遞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 捱埋個新年啦"},{"pid":"a5b6e01831a3a5bfd78455c7b8ce8fce4560c46a","tid":531772,"uid":13645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:37:23.000Z","msg":"錢到手就遞"},{"pid":"ad88e1cba8cdfb6b18a879bedc1971b8b69e7b75","tid":531772,"uid":151421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:39:06.000Z","msg":"遞左咪無花紅?  仲有食飯抽獎金可能抽起你個名，點都無得抽中。"},{"pid":"b8f4ee8bb79beac48f93a2229aaa79ab0a1ae701","tid":531772,"uid":9205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad88e1cba8cdfb6b18a879bedc1971b8b69e7b75","tid":531772,"uid":151421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:39:06.000Z","msg":"遞左咪無花紅?  仲有食飯抽獎金可能抽起你個名，點都無得抽中。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:35:25.000Z","msg":"個日朝早出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾公司 無annual dinner"},{"pid":"3bdb9fc7946fa13f3e0e6960b578eb47c69dd1c4","tid":531772,"uid":9205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5b6e01831a3a5bfd78455c7b8ce8fce4560c46a","tid":531772,"uid":13645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:37:23.000Z","msg":"錢到手就遞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:35:39.000Z","msg":"會否太串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\